	<h1><small><strong>About Bright Sparqe</strong></small></h1>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-8">			
			<p>Bright Sparqe's primary objective is to assist and provide one breakfast bag to each homeless man, woman and child. Bright Sparqe will commence the concept in the Melbourne CBD with the ultimate vision fo being a national charity.</p>
			<p>Through partherships with accredited support services Bright Sparqe will provide information and details to those who are experiencing homelessness in the community.</p>
			<p>The team at Bright Sparqe believe through this initiative it will assist the homeless in getting a good start to the day. </p>
			<p>The team at Bright Sparqe are extremely excited in how this initiative it will assist the homeless.</p>
		</div>
